headline: Can Intuitive Surgical Sustain Robust Top-line Growth in 2026?
summary: ISRG posts 20.5% revenue growth in 2025, driven by higher procedure volumes and da Vinci 5 adoption, and guides for 13-15% procedure growth in 2026.

headline: Unveiling Zimmer (ZBH) Q4 Outlook: Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Evaluate the expected performance of Zimmer (ZBH) for the quarter ended December 2025, looking beyond the conventional Wall Street top-and-bottom-line estimates and examining some of its key metrics for better insight.
